{"word":"G3727 - ὅρκος - hórkos - hor'-kos - Oath","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅρκος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hórkos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hor'-kos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Oath"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஆணை, சத்தியம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"an oath"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <b>&#x03B5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>herkos</b> (a <i>fence</i>; perhaps akin to <a href=\"#/G3725 - ὅριον - hórion - hor'-ee-on/3725\">G3725</a>); a <i>limit</i>, that is, (sacred) <i>restraint</i> (specifically <i>oath</i>): - oath."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1844 - ἐξορκίζω - exorkízō - ex-or-kid'-zo/1844\">G1844</a>, <a href=\"#/G1845 - ἐξορκιστής - exorkistḗs - ex-or-kis-tace'/1845\">G1845</a>, <a href=\"#/G1964 - ἐπιορκέω - epiorkéō - ep-ee-or-keh'-o/1964\">G1964</a>, <a href=\"#/G1965 - ἐπίορκος - epíorkos - ep-ee'-or-kos/1965\">G1965</a>, <a href=\"#/G3726 - ὁρκίζω - horkízō - hor-kid'-zo/3726\">G3726</a>, <a href=\"#/G3727 - ὅρκος - hórkos - hor'-kos/3727\">G3727</a>, <a href=\"#/G3728 - ὁρκωμοσία - horkōmosía - hor-ko-mos-ee'ah/3728\">G3728</a>"}]}